E-01 SELECT OF QUENCHING CONDITION NO. IS WRONG
E-02 NAME CODE IS NOT INPUT
E-03 NAME M/F IS NOT INPUT THAT NAME CODE APPOINTED
E-04 NAME CODE APPOINTED IS NOT USED ALREADY
E-05 MAX APPOINTED NAME CODE ARE 50. IT ALREADY OVER 50.
E-06 QTY INPUT A=PLAN-A, B=RESULT-B, C=PLAN-C
     SAME NAME CODE WAS INPUT
